### 1. Create an Agent
POST http://localhost:8000/agents/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Expert Storyteller",
    "system_prompt": "You are a creative storyteller. Tell short, engaging stories based on user prompts.",
    "voice_id": "shimmer"
}

### 2. List Agents
GET http://localhost:8000/agents/

### 3. Start a new Chat Session
POST http://localhost:8000/agents/1/sessions

### 4. List Agent Sessions
GET http://localhost:8000/agents/1/sessions

### 5. Chat within the Session (Text)
# Use the session ID from step 3 (e.g., 1)
POST http://localhost:8000/agents/1/sessions/1/chat
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="message"

Hello agent! Can you tell me a story about a brave cat?
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="generate_audio"

true
--boundary--

### 6. Get Session Details and History
GET http://localhost:8000/agents/1/sessions/1
